About

Few things about me

Fifteen Years ago, I was playing rock shows on The Vans Warped Tour. Ten years ago, I was rebuilding molten hot melters for the glass industry. Five years ago, I was creating and modifying bend programs for Amanda brake presses. Last year, I was traveling the U.S. installing commercial and residential solar racking and panels. This year, I'm looking forward to utilizing not just my work skills, but my hobby skills as well.
